    "description": "FUTURE NOIR is a first-person adventure and action game that combines elements of both first-person shooters and walking simulators. You play agent Langley, a detective in charge of solving a crime that will lead to the most remote places in a dystopian future in search of clues and evidence for his investigation. But as time passes, everything starts to get complicated and the difference between reality and imagination starts to fade, pushing Langley to the limit and to discover things that perhaps would have been better not to know.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384150/extras/e6775d6acf9a67e84b98ba012ce45b0d.poster.avif?t=1746724006\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384150/extras/e6775d6acf9a67e84b98ba012ce45b0d.webm?t=1746724006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384150/extras/e6775d6acf9a67e84b98ba012ce45b0d.mp4?t=1746724006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>THE WORLD<br><br>The game takes place on Earth, a planet in ruins that has been suffering a solar winter for decades. Humanity has spread throughout the solar system, with colonies on the Moon, Mars, Venus, and the moons of Jupiter, Saturn, and Uranus.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384150/extras/0c69fc4470b4fc937ce0ba30328e0961.poster.avif?t=1746724006\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384150/extras/0c69fc4470b4fc937ce0ba30328e0961.webm?t=1746724006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384150/extras/0c69fc4470b4fc937ce0ba30328e0961.mp4?t=1746724006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>THE GAMEPLAY<br><br>FUTURE NOIR has a unique combination of elements: first-person shooter and walking simulator mechanics mixed with adventure, exploration, action, suspense and terror, as well as interesting characters and a great story waiting to be discovered.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384150/extras/9c2c09f0f7d2ba373ffdc7cd419f6fb6.poster.avif?t=1746724006\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384150/extras/9c2c09f0f7d2ba373ffdc7cd419f6fb6.webm?t=1746724006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384150/extras/9c2c09f0f7d2ba373ffdc7cd419f6fb6.mp4?t=1746724006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
